  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/263319912e23180a4d8184870dbe184a.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/263319912e23180a4d8184870dbe184a.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/263319912e23180a4d8184870dbe184a.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> Navy War is a realistic multiplayer naval combat game of the First and Second World War!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action army games and team battles are waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steer a legendary battleship of yesteryear, use naval tactics and destroy enemy ships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Direct your fleet to glorious victory! What are you waiting for, captain?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/f38e7b3cf0a5f12d4cedb8e8bfb14509.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/f38e7b3cf0a5f12d4cedb8e8bfb14509.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/f38e7b3cf0a5f12d4cedb8e8bfb14509.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> ONLINE PvP</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting PvP naval battles - command and attack teams of players from all over the  battleship. Prove that you are the best captain in this war game and your fleet is invincible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/e68911af2aac397bbb0701805f90a5e0.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/e68911af2aac397bbb0701805f90a5e0.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/e68911af2aac397bbb0701805f90a5e0.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> VARIOUS SHIPS OF THE FIRST AND SECOND WORLD WARS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots battleships of your choice! From Aurora to Yamato! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a fraction you like and fight back against your opponent!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/25725e2834b061fb333d204b7ba9b1a0.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/25725e2834b061fb333d204b7ba9b1a0.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/25725e2834b061fb333d204b7ba9b1a0.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> TACTICAL ADVANTAGE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the warship that suits best your PvP style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When placing ships, be sure to come up with new ideas, constantly change old concepts, use flexible tactics, and improve your strategy to successfully suppress the enemy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/697bdcc83f66b0a0545cd25917751ab3.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/697bdcc83f66b0a0545cd25917751ab3.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/697bdcc83f66b0a0545cd25917751ab3.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> DEVELOP AND IMPROVE YOUR FLEET</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The upgrade systems allow you to create a unique fleet for a military sea shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve the combat characteristics of battleships, equipment, and weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use emblems, special torpedoes, and consumables to change the course of the combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> AWARDS AND TOURNAMENTS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in weekly tournaments, and win prizes and awards! Complete daily quests and challenges for even greater rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> GREAT GRAPHICS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic graphics, colorful special effects, detailed vehicles, wonderful arenas for naval battles, and the irreplaceable military spirit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready for the naval battle?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online ships are waiting for you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/263319912e23180a4d8184870dbe184a.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/263319912e23180a4d8184870dbe184a.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/263319912e23180a4d8184870dbe184a.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> Navy War is a realistic multiplayer naval combat game of the First and Second World War!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action army games and team battles are waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steer a legendary battleship of yesteryear, use naval tactics and destroy enemy ships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Direct your fleet to glorious victory! What are you waiting for, captain?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/f38e7b3cf0a5f12d4cedb8e8bfb14509.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/f38e7b3cf0a5f12d4cedb8e8bfb14509.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/f38e7b3cf0a5f12d4cedb8e8bfb14509.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> ONLINE PvP</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting PvP naval battles - command and attack teams of players from all over the  battleship. Prove that you are th