ss=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/697bdcc83f66b0a0545cd25917751ab3.poster.avif?t=1737806355\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/697bdcc83f66b0a0545cd25917751ab3.webm?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991850/extras/697bdcc83f66b0a0545cd25917751ab3.mp4?t=1737806355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> DEVELOP AND IMPROVE YOUR FLEET</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The upgrade systems allow you to create a unique fleet for a military sea shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve the combat characteristics of battleships, equipment, and weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use emblems, special torpedoes, and consumables to change the course of the combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> AWARDS AND TOURNAMENTS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in weekly tournaments, and win prizes and awards! Complete daily quests and challenges for even greater rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> GREAT GRAPHICS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic graphics, colorful special effects, detailed vehicles, wonderful arenas for naval battles, and the irreplaceable military spirit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready for the naval battle?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online ships are waiting for you!</p>",
